  <summary>An extensible mail notification service</summary>
  <summary lang="de">Ein erweiterbarer Benachrichtigungsdienst</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Bubblemail is a D-Bus service providing a list of the new and unread
      mail from local mailboxes, pop, imap, and gnome online accounts. 
      It includes a libnotify frontend to create notifications and can be used 
      by other frontends as well.
    </p>
